<inglise> Whereas, in view of the time needed to complete examination of the programmes, the time limit provided for signature of contracts in Article 1(2) of Commission Regulation (EC) No 1435/97 (3), amended by Regulation (EC) No 1035/98 (4), should be extended; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: programmide l&auml;bivaatamiseks kuluvat aega silmas pidades tuleks pikendada lepingu allkirjastamise t&auml;htaega, mis on s&auml;testatud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1435/97 (3) (muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1035/98 (4)) artikli 1 l&otilde;ikes 2; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the time limit resulting from the provision in the amended text is 1 July 1998; whereas the Regulation must therefore enter into force on the day of its publication; </inglise>
